        <h2>Estranged: Act I (Source Engine, released 2014)</h2>
        <p class="images">
            <img width="200" height="112.5" src="/sp10thewarehouse0051-thumb.jpg" alt="" />
            <img width="200" height="112.5" src="/sp01thebeginning0004-thumb.jpg" alt="" />
