        <p>Act I is the first game in the Estranged series. I started developing it mid-2011 as a Half-Life: 2 mod while I was studying at University. I published it on <a href="http://www.moddb.com/mods/estranged">ModDB</a>, and people liked it &ndash; so I carried on developing it.</p>
        <p>After releasing several alpha versions and attracting several people to work on the project, I released it on <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/app/261820">Steam</a> in January 2014 as a standalone Source Engine game for Windows, Mac and Linux.</p>
        <p>At the time of release it was translated into 26 languages, including Francés, Русский, 简体中文, 日本語, Español, Portugués and 한국의 with thanks to the amazing <a href="https://translation.steampowered.com/">Steam Translation community</a>.</p>
        <p>Act I has been downloaded by over 300,000 people since its release, and Steam users that have played it have left overwhelmingly positive feedback on the store page.</p>
        <p>Download Estranged: Act I on Steam: <a href="http://store.steampowered.com/app/261820">http://store.steampowered.com/app/261820</a></p>
